summary: THE AIR CONDITIONING ON THIS CAR IS INFERIOR TO ANY CAR THAT I HAVE OWNED BEFORE.  IT IS NOT CAPABLE OF COOLING THE INTERIOR OF THE CAR WHEN THE EXTERIOR TEMPERATURE EXCEEDS 90 DEGREES.
